\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 A}{\f0\fs24\b0 s Dr. James White states: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93There can be}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~}{\f0\fs24\b1\i1 no neutrality}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~in the universe created by the triune God, hence there can be\~}{\f0\fs24\b1\i1 no pretended place of neutrality}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~where we can stand with the unbeliever outside of the lordship of Christ. Every fact (if it is a fact) is so because Jesus made it what it is. I am called to proclaim Jesus as LORD\~}{\f0\fs24\b1\i1 not merely at the final conclusion of a long line of arguments}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~that are submitted to a rebellious creature for his approval but\~}{\f0\fs24\b1\i1 as the first and central reality that makes all knowledge and wisdom possible}{\f0\fs24\b0 .\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 [Emphasis mine]}
